Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:15.82,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}内心似被看透般颤抖不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:20.76,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}满月当空 拼命远嚎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:25.18,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}「先不要抛下我！」
